[06:41] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Web The teams that create these open-source models, they work with them and fix the bugs after the official release. Unsloth also adds dynamic 2.0 quantization. So, instead of compressing only select'

[06:54] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'layers, they dynamically adjust the quantization type of every layer with a custom scheme per model. This shrinks the model size massively while still keeping the accuracy. In plain English, it allows you to run much more powerful'

