[09:00] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'It\'s a format. It\'s a compressed ready to run version of a AI model packed into a single file so it can run fast on a normal computer. That is the plain English explanation. You can think of it like a zip file of the AI model. It\'s'

[09:12] [scene:talk]
