[09:49] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'why they fit together so naturally and so well. And llama.cpp only runs GGML. Every other format must be converted first to GGML. Now, let\'s talk about Georgi Gerganov. So, he\'s the guy who created llama.cpp, so anyone can run'

